{
  "texts": [
    "Fourth, the use of video-based annotation limits the accuracy of annotation data.",
    "We used three cameras to record participants from different angles during data collection.",
    "As it was difficult to record aspects such as the hitting sound, hitting point, and landing position during the data collection process, the annotations for Levels 3, 4, and 5 were conducted after the data collection by three annotators.",
    "The inter-rater reliability was assessed to ensure the accuracy of the annotations.",
    "The inter-rater reliability value for Level 3 was relatively low owing to the subjective nature of the hitting sound."
  ]
}